timedatectl is part of systemd and accepts options like --no-pager.

# timedatectl [status] : shows local time, UTC, hardware clock time, NTP status,
   and DST begin/end dates

# timedatectl list-timezones : list all known timezones

# timedatectl set-timezone America/New_York

# timedatectl set-time 2018-06-28 09:57:00 : sets system time (software clock)
   and real time clock (hardware clock)

# timedatectl set-local-rtc 0 : set real time clock (RTC) to UTC
